{"tid":2263428,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"螞蟻截孖展後 部份資金轉投美元  港滙突見3個月低位","createTime":"2020-10-30T01:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T05:54:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"130537b993bcee122d7a8bb6c70397bb64091b0c","tid":2263428,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201030/OGY5TM45IFAN5KVWAI25ZPWKJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201030%2FOGY5TM45IFAN5KVWAI25ZPWKJE%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KBhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=f09b139b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201030%2FOGY5TM45IFAN5KVWAI25ZPWKJE%2F&h=4c5d7f8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201030/OGY5TM45IFAN5KVWAI25ZPWKJE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻截孖展後 部份資金轉投美元 <br />\n港滙突見3個月低位<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】螞蟻（6688）孖展昨截止，金管局連日接錢行動將稍為回氣；港滙昨午突轉弱，最低兌每美元見7.7538，屬三個月低位，其後滙率回穩反彈一半。市場消息指，早前有大行預備螞蟻孖展信貸額「過龍」，截止後一下子回吐資金才拖低港滙。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：世茂、合景頭槌飛蝕百萬<br />\n<br />\n財資界指新股活動持續，資金續流向疫情控制較佳的中港地區，料年底前本港銀行體系總結餘仍會上升；由於歐洲疫情瀕失控，避險因素兼美國總統大選期間，美元不會過弱，故港滙即使維持偏強，仍不容易「日日企喺7.75」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/66qn-KjJkRjJ5hWZaLfxHfXPb-0=/1280x853/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/76QUZV7FJZHFRL434VIL3YOUF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F66qn-KjJkRjJ5hWZaLfxHfXPb-0%3D%2F1280x853%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F76QUZV7FJZHFRL434VIL3YOUF4.jpg&h=6bc556a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港滙回軟，港股昨走勢疲弱收報24586點，成交額1,331億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家：不構成港元完全轉勢<br />\n<br />\n金管局昨早紐約清晨時段，向市場注入31.78億元，經T+2結算後，今日總結餘增至4,574.63億元，續創有史以來新高。過去一個月，經該局接錢湧入的資金達1,878億元，昨晚近7時，港滙報7.7516。<br />\n<br />\n上商研究部主管林俊泓表示，港滙稍跌與螞蟻招股即將完結、預期資金將回籠市場有關，但他相。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n東亞銀行（023）高級外滙市場策略師葉澤恒則指，歐洲疫情失控加上總統選舉，重燃資。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港滙轉弱，港股昨走勢亦疲弱。在外圍影響下，恒指昨低開418點後連環跌穿10、20及50天線；其。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7ugIOGCllKDzncRnkW94i2loC8M=/539x432/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XHZXQI5MCVEV3KM57N57YLVZBE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7ugIOGCllKDzncRnkW94i2loC8M%3D%2F539x432%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXHZXQI5MCVEV3KM57N57YLVZBE.gif&h=d977e8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北水113億 逾半年來最多<br />\n<br />\n北水連續15個交易日湧入港股，昨錄淨入113.14億元，創3月19日以來最多。多隻科技股受追捧，騰訊（700）連續第三日成為吸資王，昨錄37.39億元淨入，推動股價續破頂，收報605元，升0.7%；市值增逾4,100億元至5.8萬億元。<br />\n<br />\n美團（3690）同樣強勢，錄25.74億元淨入，盤中曾破頂，收市飆6.1%至297.2元；市。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"5813bc05893dc84e1eec30270942e17185396d5f","tid":2263428,"uid":81628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T01:48:17.000Z","msg":"其實預左，終於黎料"},{"pid":"46b3fca1bbd215ac7cc758c915aee67fc07b549d","tid":2263428,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T01:57:35.000Z","msg":"又要打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49d42e8d1ce4a3ab61832af20daa1863a08b92c","tid":2263428,"uid":306621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T01:58:31.000Z","msg":"呢篇野係咪連登寫架?<br />\n連登仔: 股災呀!!!! 走鬼呀,<br />\n原來係跌 1%<br />\n<br />\n港匯變弱呀, 三個月低位呀. 原來係 7.7514<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edadfe90833bb771a2e383aeac8487b48777ab96","tid":2263428,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"日日觸發強方兌換 <br />\n有一日無觸發就叫走鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}